  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5291754">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5291754/" class="title-link">不长不短的评~</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5291754"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/ruskalulu/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u4634555-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ruskalulu/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">哈酱</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-02-03"
      class="main-meta">2012-02-03 22:55:26</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5291754_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  一本书能让人看到世界的美好，然后催人上进，这自然是一本好书。而一本书在叫你尽识人间丑恶的同时，却让你仍然相信美好的存在，这便是《麒麟》。《麒麟》，是不老不死的深刻爱情，是护疆爱国的铮铮铁骨，是理解却不意味着认同的人生态度，是看破黑暗挣向光明的坚定执着。这是...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5291754_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5291754_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评4篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
